sandorex added a cross-platform 
``kill``
 command (#1326)
thegedge fixed some issues in 
``from-ssv``
 (#1334)
andrasio removed some unnecessary build dependencies (#1335)
twitu fixed issues in 
``cp``
 (#1339)
